gantt
  title Commerce platform 1.0 release plan
  dateFormat YYYY-MM-DD
  axisFormat %b %d
  excludes weekends
  todayMarker off

  section Discovery
  Customer interviews          :done, interviews, 2026-07-01, 4d
  Architecture decision        :done, architecture, after interviews, 3d
  Release scope approved       :milestone, scope, after architecture, 0d

  section Build
  Checkout experience          :done, checkout, after scope, 7d
  Order API                    :active, order_api, after scope, 9d
  Fulfillment integration      :active, fulfillment, after architecture, 8d
  Observability dashboards     :observability, after order_api, 3d

  section Validate
  End-to-end test campaign     :crit, e2e, after checkout order_api fulfillment, 4d
  Performance acceptance       :crit, performance, after e2e, 3d
  Release candidate            :milestone, rc, after performance, 0d

  section Launch
  Operations readiness review  :crit, readiness, after rc observability, 2d
  Production rollout           :crit, rollout, after readiness, 2d
  Version 1.0 available        :milestone, release, after rollout, 0d
